latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Creating memories with my little one is my favorite thing to do! ☺️ I keep looking for new, fun ways to make his day better. That is why today we tried this super exciting activity that I found for Taanish. We participated in the #TinyBowlTales contest by @nestleceregrow and made our own version of the Ceregrow bowl. 🙌

Not only did we decorate the entire bowl with our favorite fruits, but we also learned about different shapes while we were in the process of making the bowl. Fun and learning, all together! ❤️🥰

If you are also planning a fun evening with your kids, then do try making a bowl art with your munchkins. I’m looking forward to seeing what the theme of your Ceregrow bowl is and how you are planning to decorate it. Share it with me in the comment section down below. 💖

Don’t forget to tag @nestleceregrow and use the hashtag #TinyBowlTales, and win some exciting prizes! :D
